    "## Help and Troubleshooting\n",
    "\n",
    "### Handling OAuth Consent Screen Issues\n",
    "\n",
    "If you see \"App not verified\" warnings:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Go to [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/)\n",
    "2. Select your project\n",
    "3. Go to \"APIs & Services\" > \"OAuth consent screen\"\n",
    "4. Add your email as a test user\n",
    "5. Save changes\n",
    "6. When authenticating, click \"Advanced\" and then \"Go to [app name] (unsafe)\"\n",
    "\n",
    "### Finding Your Calendar URL\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Outlook**: Go to calendar settings > Shared Calendars > Publish Calendar > Copy the ICS link\n",
    "- **iCloud**: Go to calendar settings > Share Calendar > Public Calendar > Copy the link\n",
    "- **Google Calendar**: Go to calendar settings > Integrate calendar > Secret address in iCal format\n",
    "\n",
    "For more detailed help, please refer to the README.md file."
   ]
